data.description: Beautiful and modern American West home in the heart of Southwest. Open floorplan with spacious living room connected to the dining area and the kitchen. White freshly painted cabinets with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Tiles and brand new laminate flooring throughout. Alarm prewired. Spacious Main bedroom with large walk-in closet, separate tub and shower. Fabulous pool in the backyard. Five minute walk to Cougar Creek Park. Centrally located to several amenities, schools, freeway, shopping, and dining.
